245
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,960
Why like a dog?

246
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:03,240
Because you have family and you don't sit alone on the holiday.

247
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:06,040
How do you know he'll be alone? Maybe he'll have a girl with him?

248
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,600
Pinchas, do me a favor,

249
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:09,840
you know very well what kind of girls are out there

250
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:12,960
not at their family's house on holiday evening.

251
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:15,120
Oh really? Well, not good girls.

252
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:17,640
But that's exactly the type I like. Well, whatever. Forget it, Adam,

253
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:19,680
anyway, you're also invited to my family.

254
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:21,680
Shani, I love you, it’s not about that,

255
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:24,440
