256
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,720
Shani, I’m really sorry,

257
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:30,320
tell Mom thank you very much, but we can’t make it this year.

258
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:31,960
No way.

259
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:35,360
Riki, I don’t understand, what, are you three just going to sit alone on the holiday?

260
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:39,680
Yeah. Adam, Dad, and me. Well, just the three of you? That’s a little,

261
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:41,160
isn’t that a bit sad?

262
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:44,120
No, this way we’ll have quality time with Adam.

263
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:47,640
Did you know Bazir loved to wear women’s clothes?

264
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:49,880
Yeah, that’s known.

265
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:54,000
So tell me, Shani, is the food at your place good? Totally amazing.

266
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:59,480
I swear to you, Smadar won’t come here. It’s just my mom and her nonsense.

267
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:02,160
Listen, Shani... well, then focus on the Maldives and a new swimsuit,

268
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:04,600
