334
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:55,800
Okay, Riki.

335
00:14:57,520 --> 00:14:58,640
Come on. Why are you being a jerk?

336
00:14:58,720 --> 00:15:01,120
One day you’ll be my husband. What do you want from me?

337
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:03,720
Besides, I could’ve had a solo vacation,

338
00:15:03,880 --> 00:15:05,040
Orna ruined that with Mom.

339
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,440
Hey, Grandpa. Hey, Raz.

340
00:15:06,920 --> 00:15:09,320
Come on, Lian, come here, come to Grandpa. Don’t change the subject now.

341
00:15:09,880 --> 00:15:12,720
Hey, I knocked but you didn’t answer.

342
00:15:13,280 --> 00:15:15,400
Smadar, so nice you came.

343
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:16,760
Hi, Smadar. Hey.

344
00:15:16,920 --> 00:15:18,080
Hi, Smadar. Hey.

345
00:15:18,640 --> 00:15:20,280
Still a blonde, I see.

346
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:23,960
How’s it going? It was good until I met you.

347
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:26,880
Smadar. Hey, Roko.

348
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:28,160
Oh, wow.

349
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:31,640
So nice you arrived, how are you?

350
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,600
I’m good, thanks, and you?

351
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:35,760
I’m healthy, thanks. So, what’s up?

352
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:37,800
At home, look who’s here.

353
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:39,480
Oh, hey, so... sit down.

354
00:15:39,560 --> 00:15:41,120
Hi, Smadar. Hey.

355
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:43,960
Mom, I think my shirt ripped...

356
00:15:44,680 --> 00:15:47,000
Oh, Smadar, what are you doing here? Why did you come up?

357
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:49,120
You said you’d call. I would’ve come down. For what...

358
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:51,360
Why didn’t you call? I would’ve come down right away to get you.

359
00:15:51,440 --> 00:15:52,600
Yeah, I tried to call

360
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:54,680
