361
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:56,360
What do you mean it's closed, never!

362
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:58,440
Where's the... you know, is this a place?

363
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:00,920
It's really closed. Come on, please.

364
00:16:01,280 --> 00:16:04,760
How are you, Smadar? You look great.

365
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:07,120
Thanks, Pinchas, you too.

366
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:10,000
Smadar, come on, sit here, why are you standing?

367
00:16:10,080 --> 00:16:11,920
No, no, no, I'm leaving, I'm leaving.

368
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:14,640
Itamar, can I have a quick word with you?

369
00:16:14,800 --> 00:16:16,920
Sure, what's the problem? Let's go to the balcony like usual,

370
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:18,880
