371
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:20,080
Unfortunately.

372
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:30,440
She looks... great. Yeah, right.

373
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:34,040
Itamar Tzafan and Smadar Malda.

374
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:39,160
What's up?

375
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:42,640
It's about the kids for the holiday. So, I wanted to talk to you about that.

376
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:43,800
Yeah? So listen,

377
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:45,760
I’d really love it if they could be with me for Rosh Hashanah,

378
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:47,920
my mom is getting cozy. For Rosh Hashanah?

379
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:50,280
Yeah, I know it's a religious thing, but are you okay with that?

380
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:52,040
Of course, of course. So,

381
00:16:52,520 --> 00:16:54,800
because for Sukkot, Gilan and I are planning to go to the Maldives

382
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:57,120
with my mom and the kids for the whole week of Sukkot.

383
00:16:57,200 --> 00:16:59,080
Yeah. Gilan has a place there, so... cheers to him.

384
00:16:59,160 --> 00:17:00,000
Yeah.

385
00:17:01,520 --> 00:17:04,960
And cheers to you, a week with the kids in the Maldives and your mom.

386
00:17:05,040 --> 00:17:06,160
It's like...

387
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:09,359
Good for you, I haven't really been in touch with the kids lately.

388
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:10,280
Me neither.

389
00:17:10,839 --> 00:17:12,359
Did you see Raz's girlfriend?

390
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:15,240
I saw her and regretted it immediately.

391
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:19,880
With your mom, that's a double whammy.

392
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:23,760
Yeah.

393
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:25,920
I wonder what they're talking about, huh?

394
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:27,800
Come on, it's not nice to eavesdrop like that.

395
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,480
Leave them alone, it's none of our business.

396
00:17:30,120 --> 00:17:32,800
Did you talk to Mom? Wait, maybe Itamar wants to switch with her?

397
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:35,200
No way, no chance, you don't know Smadar.

398
00:17:35,800 --> 00:17:37,840
But she looks... okay, we get it, Pinchas, she looks amazing.

399
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:40,960
I think she wants Itamar back.

400
00:17:41,040 --> 00:17:43,240
Riki, maybe you forgot, but Itamar is mine.

401
00:17:43,360 --> 00:17:44,880
Why are you putting words in my mouth?

402
00:17:45,040 --> 00:17:48,600
I didn't say he wants you, I said she wants you.

403
00:17:48,680 --> 00:17:50,120
Are we eating today too?

404
00:17:53,360 --> 00:17:55,080
I don't understand a word of what she's saying either.

405
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:57,760
And if I manage to understand, I don't get what I understood.

406
00:17:58,720 --> 00:18:00,920
Well, it's not hard to say things you don't understand at all.

407
00:18:02,240 --> 00:18:04,680
I didn't get it. We're just joking with you.

408
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:10,320
Sorry, I don't want to interrupt. Of course not.

409
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:14,400
Smadar, my dear, why don't you stay and eat with us?

410
00:18:14,800 --> 00:18:16,160
I'm defrosting.

411
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:20,120
Wow, I miss your shleiker so much, wow.

412
00:18:20,760 --> 00:18:22,480
What, is that going to bother you? Look...

413
00:18:22,600 --> 00:18:23,880
No way.

414
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:26,080
Alright, fine, whatever.

415
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:27,440
Gilan is playing soccer.

416
00:18:27,560 --> 00:18:30,120
How fun, I'm excited.

417
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:32,600
How fun, just like old times, my boy.

418
00:18:35,560 --> 00:18:36,680
Amazing kids.

419
00:18:40,360 --> 00:18:41,360
Alright,

420
00:18:41,840 --> 00:18:43,240
I'm going to set the table.

421
00:18:43,320 --> 00:18:45,040
What, she's in shock? Yeah, totally.

422
00:18:45,600 --> 00:18:47,960
Itamar, come here for a sec. Sure thing.

423
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:54,960
So what, gas, huh? Yeah, right.

424
00:18:58,920 --> 00:19:01,400
Alright, I'm gonna help Riki with the kids.

425
00:19:07,720 --> 00:19:09,040
Why is your mom doing this to me?

426
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:10,920
Babe, Smadar just came to tell me

427
00:19:11,040 --> 00:19:13,040
