428
00:19:13,160 --> 00:19:14,360
So why is she in shock?

429
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:16,360
Michali, babe, it's okay. No, it's not.

430
00:19:16,440 --> 00:19:19,560
Of course, it's fine from your side, but from Riki's side, it's totally not okay.

431
00:19:19,640 --> 00:19:21,200
Come on, what? This time she really overdid it a bit.

432
00:19:21,280 --> 00:19:23,480
What are you doing here? I just took the kid to the bathroom.

433
00:19:23,600 --> 00:19:25,680
Michali, I'm telling you, there's no reason to get upset and cry.

434
00:19:25,760 --> 00:19:27,040
No, sorry, it's her right.

435
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:29,520
No, I mean, don’t give my mom the pleasure of seeing you like this,

436
00:19:29,600 --> 00:19:31,280
like she beat you, fight back.

437
00:19:31,360 --> 00:19:34,480
Yeah, if you're like a thorn in the throat, be a thorn in the throat. Right, thorn in the throat.

438
00:19:34,600 --> 00:19:36,120
What, are you all here? Why did you come?

439
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:39,200
Dad sent me to check if everything's okay. Everything's fine.

440
00:19:39,280 --> 00:19:41,440
Exactly, everything's fine, don’t be afraid of anyone.

441
00:19:41,520 --> 00:19:43,480
This time she really overdid it. Totally.

442
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:44,320
Dad.

443
00:19:44,400 --> 00:19:46,840
Are you guys normal? I'm totally here alone.

444
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:48,480
Come on.

445
00:19:48,560 --> 00:19:50,840
And Shani, about your mom, we are going for the holiday after all.

446
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:51,880
Really? Yeah.

447
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:53,000
<i>What a mess</i>

448
00:19:53,080 --> 00:19:54,760
Great. Babe. Babe.

449
00:19:56,560 --> 00:19:58,760
Alright, Riki, I think I’ll head out, I’m just making a mess.

450
00:19:59,600 --> 00:20:02,000
What would we do without all this chaos?

451
00:20:02,560 --> 00:20:05,480
The bigger the mess, the bigger the personality.

452
00:20:06,800 --> 00:20:08,760
Just like all your jokes, funny and whiny.

453
00:20:08,840 --> 00:20:12,160
Oh, you're so sensitive that you're leaving because of the...

454
00:20:12,240 --> 00:20:13,600
Meital. Michal.

455
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:14,800
Michal, Michal.

456
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:18,080
Just know you'll always be like my daughter.

457
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:21,160
This is like home.

458
00:20:26,160 --> 00:20:27,360
Come in, come in.

459
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:36,720
Come on.

460
00:20:37,160 --> 00:20:38,160
Alright, I'm out.

461
00:20:38,840 --> 00:20:40,440
<i>What a mess</i>

462
00:20:40,520 --> 00:20:42,360
So what, for the holiday, you're with the kids at your mom's?

463
00:20:42,520 --> 00:20:46,880
Big suffering, huh? Yeah, but on the other hand, a week in the Maldives after that.

464
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:49,920
What a coincidence, Itamar and Michal will be in the Maldives too.

465
00:20:50,520 --> 00:20:52,440
When? Rosh Hashanah.

466
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:54,360
What, you can't,

467
