469
00:21:00,080 --> 00:21:02,560
Alright, bye. Bye, bye.

470
00:21:02,680 --> 00:21:03,640
<i>What a mess</i>

471
00:21:04,280 --> 00:21:05,960
I knew everything was too good to be true.

472
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:08,240
You're not spending the holiday alone.

473
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:11,080
And what about me? We're doing the holiday here.

474
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:14,480
Sorry, Riki, but this year we're doing the holiday at my mom's.

475
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:16,920
No, but... at my mom's!

476
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:19,480
There's a good chance we'll be in a mess the next day.

477
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:24,800
You said she would cause problems.

478
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:26,520
What problems, Mom? Come on, really,

479
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:27,960
